Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{Mayo Chiki}{arashi0 partA}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.94,0:02:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(850,0)\fnGentium Book Basic\fs90\be5\pos(650,305)\c&HFDFEFA&\3c&H46A851&}Go Out With Me
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.22,0:00:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, those meat balls look tasty!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.26,0:00:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me one.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.28,0:00:04.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, here you go!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.12,0:00:06.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll trade you my tamagoyaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.12,0:00:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you going to stop by the station on your way home?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.86,0:00:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard the new macaroon is on sale.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.89,0:00:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a good color after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.98,0:00:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Does it use gloss?{Is it lipgloss?}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.78,0:00:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,No, just the lip.{No, just lipstick.}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.30,0:00:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,How nice! Where did you buy it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.04,0:02:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{OP}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.05,0:02:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Get out of the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.15,0:02:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.79,0:02:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahhh, I thought I was dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.40,0:02:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm? My glasses?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.22,0:02:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Crap, that probably would have been my deathbed!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.06,0:02:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,My school's uniform?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.02,0:03:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Umm, hello...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.05,0:03:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness, she's alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.31,0:03:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What should I do? I crashed into a person!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.04,0:03:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to call the police!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.35,0:03:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'll just pretend it didn't happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.08,0:03:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm actually fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.78,0:03:31.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Wah! Why are you still alive?{How are you still alive?}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.51,0:03:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,A-Are you truly human?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.48,0:03:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You're quite the rude one.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.55,0:03:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,My body can withstand more than an average person thanks to circumstances at my house.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.11,0:03:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a student at my school, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.49,0:03:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.44,0:03:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you asking me that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.46,0:03:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It was an accident after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.98,0:03:47.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I should at least know your name, shouldn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.02,0:03:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I don't want to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.23,0:03:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Then what year are you in?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.89,0:03:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Second year.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.20,0:03:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,So, the same as me. What class are you in?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.37,0:04:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did it have to end up there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.13,0:04:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey, what are you looking at?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.67,0:04:07.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, there's something I want down there...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.04,0:04:09.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Something you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.97,0:04:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a bit hard for me to retrieve it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.53,0:04:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you get it for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.41,0:04:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Why should I do such a thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.40,0:04:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't want to, I could get it myself, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.10,0:04:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? Wait, could it be...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.59,0:04:26.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.27,0:04:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,NO!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.92,0:04:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.22,0:04:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up, you pervert! Why would I let you strip me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.29,0:04:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Strip you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.44,0:04:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Die! Eat shit and die!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.97,0:04:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? W-
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.50,0:04:47.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Woah! That was close...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.96,0:04:48.89,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.22,0:04:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,My glasses.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.60,0:04:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Could it be...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.91,0:04:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,That was what you wanted to get?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.32,0:04:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. What the heck did you think I wanted?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.95,0:05:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Why didn't I realize it before?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.88,0:05:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Pink~
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.85,0:05:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not much of a fight, even though you're her older brother are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.20,0:05:20.69,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you know about Kureha-
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.52,0:05:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I really, REALLY can't believe this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.56,0:05:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Why does it have to be you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.32,0:05:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It's coming out... Something's coming out!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.47,0:05:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.25,0:05:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Why does someone like you...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.24,0:05:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,have to be Subaru-sama's friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.36,0:05:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.00,0:05:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Since I asked you, I'll tell you my name as well. I'm Usami.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.89,0:05:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Rabbit?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.62,0:05:54.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Not "Rabbit!" I'm a Roran Academy second-year, member of the textile arts club.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.56,0:05:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Usami Masamune!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.94,0:05:58.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Textile arts club, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.95,0:06:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Nurse's Office
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.59,0:06:03.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.58,0:06:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn, that girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.84,0:06:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.26,0:06:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?{Are you all right?}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.09,0:06:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Konoe?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.04,0:06:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Jirou, I was startled!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.04,0:06:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{Finding you lying face-down on the road was surprising.}I was surprised to have found you lying face-down on the road.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.19,0:06:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I even brought you to the academy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.95,0:06:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Were you hit by a car?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.09,0:06:23.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.29,0:06:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.27,0:06:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm all right. I didn't get hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.79,0:06:29.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. If you say so, then it's fine, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.47,0:06:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, Jirou, you said things in your sleep that I couldn't quite understand...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.53,0:06:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Sleeptalking?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.48,0:06:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,"Please forgive me, my queen!"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.06,0:06:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,"If you keep stretching me like this, I might start to see a whole new world!"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.34,0:06:45.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Or like,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.19,0:06:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,"I'll give it back! Please forgive me already! Oh my lord!"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.78,0:06:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,And there is...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.87,0:06:54.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What she did earlier went straight to my subconscious!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.00,0:06:57.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Could it be that your heart is in turmoil?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.52,0:06:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.90,0:07:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that I think about it, where's Suzutsuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.99,0:07:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Wasn't she with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.67,0:07:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,She's in class.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.88,0:07:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.87,0:07:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you been avoiding her?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.58,0:07:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,,To be more precise, ever since the end of the Golden Week.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.82,0:07:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,,If you have something that is bothering you, then tell me about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.38,0:07:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,We're friends, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.71,0:07:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I can at least give you some advice since we're friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.03,0:07:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Konoe!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.69,0:07:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,But there is one condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.66,0:07:37.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Condition?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.87,0:07:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you to go with me to the school festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.48,0:07:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,School festival?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.79,0:07:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Ojou-sama seems to be busy organizing the event.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.66,0:07:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I was told to enjoy the festival and not worry about her, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.28,0:07:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know how to have fun at a school festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.77,0:08:03.19,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I want you to go to the school festival with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.35,0:08:06.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You're such a fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.51,0:08:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.10,0:08:11.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go together, to the school festival!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.91,0:08:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.31,0:08:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I am sure it'll be a fun school festival!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.42,0:08:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.98,0:08:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. I will listen to whatever is bothering you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.78,0:08:26.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Let’s see...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.25,0:08:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't need to be so stiff!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.10,0:08:32.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Please listen to me without jumping to conclusions.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.28,0:08:34.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a butler.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.47,0:08:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't get startled by the little things.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.49,0:08:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Say whatever you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.84,0:08:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, here I go!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.36,0:08:43.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, it's about my first kiss.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.99,0:08:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you saying such things now?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.79,0:08:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Could it be, Ojou-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.95,0:08:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I was surprised, because it was rather sudden.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.20,0:08:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I am surprised as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.55,0:09:00.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Because that was my first!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.28,0:09:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,She said the same, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.08,0:09:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it the truth?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.17,0:09:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't say foolish things!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.86,0:09:10.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It really was my first time!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.11,0:09:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course! My bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.58,0:09:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish I had a chance to do this all over again.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.18,0:09:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.51,0:09:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Like I said, I wish I had a chance to do this all over again.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.34,0:09:25.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to do it again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.03,0:09:27.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.57,0:09:28.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now!?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.82,0:09:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we certainly {\i1}are{\i0} alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.62,0:09:37.81,Default,,0,0,0,,But I still can't accept that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.28,0:09:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.09,0:09:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,At any rate, why...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.30,0:09:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.35,0:09:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.34,0:09:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're going to do it, then do it fast!{If you're going to do it, then hurry up! - Need raw to be sure}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.81,0:09:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Do what?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.88,0:10:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I never thought you were such an uncooperative person!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.61,0:10:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you going on about?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.65,0:10:04.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Like you said, a kiss.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.26,0:10:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You said you wanted to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.02,0:10:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh...what?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.34,0:10:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Here I go!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.90,0:10:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.27,0:10:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Ojou-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.20,0:10:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,This is not what you think.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.32,0:10:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't mind what you do,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.15,0:10:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,but please be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.52,0:10:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,In this place you are a male, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.77,0:10:30.99,Default,,0,0,0,,My deepest apologies!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.99,0:10:32.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Morning, Jirou-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.89,0:10:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel like it has been a while since we have spoken like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.38,0:10:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to go back to class ahead of you guys.{I'm going to head back to class before you guys.}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.80,0:10:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I won't let you escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.41,0:10:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Bitch, you know I'm gynophobic!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.02,0:10:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,And this is part of your therapy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.89,0:10:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You came all this way to do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.19,0:10:54.97,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.33,0:10:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Our class finally decided on what to do...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.04,0:10:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,So I came to tell you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.06,0:10:59.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.53,0:11:02.17,Default,,0,0,0,,A Crossplay Café!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.55,0:11:03.45,Default,,0,0,0,,A Crossplay Café?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.02,0:11:08.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone wants to see Subaru cross-dress.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.87,0:11:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You like to dress up cute,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.03,0:11:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.16,0:11:17.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Now then...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.82,0:11:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You dropped something.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.06,0:11:21.31,Default,,0,0,0,,That was inside my shoe locker.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.95,0:11:23.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You received a love letter in this day and age?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.31,0:11:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.92,0:11:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Of what?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.42,0:11:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What would you think if I were to accept the confession?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.05,0:11:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I don't think there's a problem if you go out with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.32,0:11:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.23,0:11:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Say Subaru, what would you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.74,0:11:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,If I were forcibly kissed by the sender of this love letter?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.40,0:11:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I would kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.65,0:11:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I would never forgive anyone who would do that to Ojou-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.19,0:11:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Subaru-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.55,0:11:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I can count on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.45,0:11:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right, Jirou-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.39,0:11:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You look a bit pale!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.65,0:11:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want to take some aspirin?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.91,0:12:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll even give it to you mouth-to-mouth
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.73,0:12:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, I will see you later, Jirou-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.87,0:12:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,After I have declined the confession, I will return to the classroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.65,0:12:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.41,0:12:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,This all happened because of her!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.62,0:12:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you, you ill-mannered rabbit!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.43,0:12:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is ill-mannered?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.92,0:12:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.20,0:12:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I have important things to talk to you about!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.88,0:12:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{Mayo Chiki}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.52,0:12:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Dododko dodosko, mayiichuunyuu!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.23,0:12:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Do these knee-highs and this slender upper body belong to Konoe? What?! It's me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.82,0:12:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{Mayo Chiki}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.43,0:12:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Go out with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.06,0:12:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.96,0:12:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Not, "What?" I'm telling you to go out with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.64,0:12:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,To be more precise, I want you to pretend to be my boyfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.73,0:12:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,At least until the end of the school festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.56,0:12:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me tell you right now; you do not have any right to refuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.95,0:12:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What's your problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.92,0:13:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there something you have a problem with?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.39,0:13:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.70,0:13:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You called me out here just to mess with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.83,0:13:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It's obvious that I called you here for a serious conversation.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.66,0:13:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my favorite spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.29,0:13:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,This is where I can be alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.45,0:13:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.01,0:13:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,This is where I saw Subaru-sama for the first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.45,0:13:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,To be honest, it was love at first sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.04,0:13:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.94,0:13:30.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know what S4 is?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.99,0:13:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Konoe's biggest fan club in the school right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.69,0:13:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,S4...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.52,0:13:37.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Shooting Star Subaru-Sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.99,0:13:40.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a member of that group.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.75,0:13:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's why she was acting that way earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.36,0:13:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,During this year's school festival, there's a secret S4 event.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.68,0:13:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean by a secret event?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.81,0:13:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,A war.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.26,0:13:59.61,Default,,0,0,0,,We, the S4 and the Watching Over Subaru-Sama club are going to have an all-out war.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.08,0:14:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What does that have to do with me going out with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.07,0:14:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,If you, who is believed to be dating Subaru-sama, are now going out with a girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.20,0:14:15.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll shake up the other group that wants a Boys-Love relationship.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.35,0:14:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,So you do understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.11,0:14:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,But I don't get why I have to take part in this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.58,0:14:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, I won't ask you to do this for free.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.22,0:14:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,When we win, I'll vouch for you and tell them not to touch you ever again.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.60,0:14:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What? You don't want that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.12,0:14:34.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you dissatisfied with my looks?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.68,0:14:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you're really cute, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.82,0:14:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,R-really?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.77,0:14:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,T-then it should be fine, shouldn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.33,0:14:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it'd still be a problem for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.47,0:14:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Sakamachi Kinjirou!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.72,0:14:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Sakama Chicken Jirou!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.31,0:14:51.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't call me by my full name!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.62,0:14:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,A chicken, just like your name.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.14,0:14:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you that afraid of angering Subaru-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.70,0:14:58.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Why would I anger Subaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.27,0:14:59.43,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no use in playing dumb.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.53,0:15:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The reason S4 and Watching Over Subaru-Sama are fighting is because you're going out with Subaru-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.96,0:15:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm telling you, that's a misunderstanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.63,0:15:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,But you guys are so friendly with one another.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.07,0:15:12.09,Default,,0,0,0,,And you guys eat lunch together.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.09,0:15:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? That's normal for friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.91,0:15:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Subaru-sama isn't normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.02,0:15:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Other than his master, Kanade, he stays away from everyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.25,0:15:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,But you, she let you get close to her for some reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.70,0:15:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,That in and of itself is abnormal...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.57,0:15:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.33,0:15:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I have proof.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.01,0:15:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Where were you looking from?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.58,0:15:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,When I went out shopping,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.72,0:15:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I happened to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.60,0:15:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You gave him a stuffed animal as a present.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.09,0:15:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,And it looked like you were about to embrace him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.48,0:15:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that's... uh... my...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.36,0:15:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.95,0:15:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It's your hobby, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.43,0:15:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,If you didn't make him do such a thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.66,0:15:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Subaru-sama is acting more feminine...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.55,0:15:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{Rumors about his feminine side are spreading...}There are rumors spreading about his feminine side...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.35,0:16:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,If they find out she's a girl, Konoe will be...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.01,0:16:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.82,0:16:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I made Konoe do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.95,0:16:08.33,Default,,0,0,0,,So delete that picture!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.69,0:16:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't get off that easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.52,0:16:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You have no choice but to go along with my plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.84,0:16:16.81,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't, I'll spread this picture around the whole school.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.85,0:16:19.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Jirou?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.87,0:16:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Konoe? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.35,0:16:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I was looking for you because you weren't in class.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.53,0:16:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's that girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.81,0:16:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Shu-Shu-Shubaru-sama...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.97,0:16:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, say something.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.94,0:16:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't expect a normal student like me to converse with him!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.45,0:16:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You explain it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.95,0:16:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean by "you explain it"?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.80,0:16:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Just say that you're my boyfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.63,0:16:42.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.53,0:16:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you two whispering about?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.19,0:16:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll introduce you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.54,0:16:49.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Her name is Usami Masamune.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.42,0:16:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,This might sound sudden, but we're dating.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.00,0:16:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not a very funny joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.85,0:17:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Konoe...um...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.30,0:17:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you to Jirou?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.88,0:17:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you say something?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.71,0:17:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,We're really dating!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.51,0:17:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,We even promised to be alone together during the school festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.12,0:17:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.43,0:17:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Jirou, is that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.13,0:17:20.39,Default,,0,0,0,,During the school festival, you're going to be on a date with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.06,0:17:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.60,0:17:34.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You even promised...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.52,0:17:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Jirou, you liar!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.01,0:17:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Ko-Ko-Ko-Ko-Konoe...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.21,0:17:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.73,0:17:47.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll pretend I'm your boyfriend until the end of the school festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.61,0:17:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,So don't spread that picture around.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.14,0:17:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I know...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.18,0:17:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Then after school, let's practice dating.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.08,0:18:01.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Since you're my boyfriend, go shopping with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.35,0:18:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to buy something for the school festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.49,0:18:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What is Class B doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.70,0:18:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,,A swimsuit café.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.77,0:18:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,A scorching hot adventure!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.57,0:18:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,A swimsuit café?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.12,0:18:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I'm buying a swimsuit.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.66,0:18:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Then go shopping with your female classmates.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.22,0:18:18.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have any friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.88,0:18:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Time to try it on.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.36,0:18:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You can come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.34,0:18:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,But only your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.62,0:18:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.57,0:18:32.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You're my boyfriend, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.73,0:18:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to barge in!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.07,0:18:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,How is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.76,0:18:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Weren't there any other ones, like a bikini?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.54,0:18:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,How could I wear such a thing in front of my classmates?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.98,0:18:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it isn't bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.47,0:18:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.49,0:18:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I'll go with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.68,0:18:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't take your head out now, I'll cut it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.57,0:18:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Buy this for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.55,0:18:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Why should I?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.38,0:19:05.93,Default,,0,0,0,,B-Because I'm not even in the swimming club and if I bought this full-blown swimsuit, it'd be embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.93,0:19:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What if they think I have some weird hobby?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.55,0:19:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not in the swimming club nor am I a girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.04,0:19:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Buy it yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.06,0:19:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Just buy it for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.51,0:19:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I refuse!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.24,0:19:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.00,0:19:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.55,0:19:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,This swimsuit is kind of warm.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.59,0:19:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,She just wore this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.06,0:19:22.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you being silent for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.87,0:19:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not smelling it, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.00,0:19:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Idiot! Pervert!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.98,0:19:27.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Like I'd do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.38,0:19:28.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Here...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.10,0:19:43.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going this way...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.62,0:19:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,The train station is that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.86,0:19:46.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm walking home.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.04,0:19:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It would take at least an hour from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.54,0:19:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a waste of a train ticket.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.75,0:19:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,And I need money to repair my bike.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.34,0:19:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to be frugal this month.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.05,0:19:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.88,0:20:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll walk home too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.69,0:20:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been skipping training.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.23,0:20:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll get home late.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.51,0:20:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, Kureha said that she'd be late because of the school festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.45,0:20:16.99,Default,,0,0,0,,How about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.35,0:20:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.63,0:20:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't really matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.29,0:20:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no point in going home early.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.16,0:20:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Sakamachi Kinjirou.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.77,0:20:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.05,0:20:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Sakama Chicken Jirou.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.78,0:20:35.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Like I said, don't call me by my full name.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.92,0:20:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to think of what to call each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.75,0:20:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to be friendly with one another or it'll be awkward.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.29,0:20:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Friendly...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.00,0:20:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Usamin!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.59,0:20:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want to get kicked off of here?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.06,0:20:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,No, please don't! Really!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.70,0:20:53.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, until the school festival ends, you and I are dating.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.30,0:20:56.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Which means we're lovers right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.80,0:20:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Then promise me one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.53,0:20:59.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Promise?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.08,0:21:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter what happens...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.12,0:21:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Believe in me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.59,0:21:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.04,0:21:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll believe in you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.94,0:21:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.74,0:21:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Believe in me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.77,0:21:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, I'll believe in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.26,0:21:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.09,0:21:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Usami is fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.07,0:21:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.37,0:21:26.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Call me by that name.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.60,0:21:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't need to add the honorifics.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.62,0:21:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Friendly?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.36,0:21:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,That's fine with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.73,0:21:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You're Idiot-chicken.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.42,0:21:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.82,0:21:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Idiot-chicken.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.99,0:21:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Being an idiot and a chicken, doesn't that suit you perfectly?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.17,0:21:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What about it suits me perfectly?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.03,0:21:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be counting on you Idiot-chicken.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.80,0:21:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,That's name-calling!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.90,0:23:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{ed}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.72,0:23:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Jirou-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.31,0:23:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to do something that starts with "S."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.67,0:23:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Start the laundry?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.82,0:23:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.01,0:23:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Something more tempting.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.60,0:23:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Shakespeare!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.60,0:23:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Something more exciting.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.29,0:23:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... sexual harassment?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.83,0:23:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm already doing that to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.73,0:23:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You are?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.82,0:24:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you don't have personal experience...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.86,0:24:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.62,0:24:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Se-Se-!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.26,0:24:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time on Mayo Chiki:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.61,0:24:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,The Sixth Story: Let's Start a War.
